Romola Garai https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romola_Garai 0 Romola Sadie Garai (; born 6 August 1982) is a British film and television actress. She appeared in Amazing Grace, Atonement, and Glorious 39, and in the BBC series Emma, The Hour and The Crimson Petal and the White. She has been nominated for a Golden Globe Award twice and for a BAFTA award. Romola_Sadie_Garai ( ; born 6_August_1982 ) is a_British_film_and_television_actress .
